logenetically informed comparisons of the two clades, we did find weak evidence in support of this hypothesis. We conclude that bat brains show evidence of adaptation to foraging ecology.", "access_right": "restricted", "creators": [{"name": "Hutcheon, James M.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Kirsch, John A.W.", "affiliation": null}, {"name": "Garland Jr, Theodore", "affiliation": null}], "keywords": ["Biodiversity", "Mammalia", "Chiroptera", "Chordata", "Animalia", "bats", "bat"], "related_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/64470a6f9de0927a7498c731afaf35f5", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://sha256/401665c6e2179517a0ee3e60c657fe27c20e36f81e10dd36eada1fde14267c97", "relation": "hasVersion", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "zotero://select/groups/5435545/items/68YK2XWS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://zotero.org/groups/5435545/items/68YK2XWS", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "https://linker.bio/cut:hash://md5/15af0dd7a91ff634a1d00d02b4d934cd!/b261626-264095", "relation": "isDerivedFrom", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "hash://md5/ce1e7618f237ff56e74d51f496e811a3", "relation": "isPartOf", "scheme": "url"}, {"identifier": "10.5281/zenodo.1410543", "relation": "isCompiledBy", "resource_type": "software", "scheme": "doi"}], "custom": {"dwc:class": ["Mammalia"], "dwc:kingdom": ["Animalia"], "dwc:order": ["Chiroptera"], "dwc:phylum": ["Chordata"]}, "resource_type": {"title": "Journal article", "type": "publication", "subtype": "article"}, "journal": {"issue": "3", "pages": "165-180", "title": "Brain, Behavior and Evolution", "volume": "60"}, "alternate_identifiers": [{"identifier": "hash://md5/64470a6f9de0927a7498c731afaf35f5"}, {"identifier": "urn:lsid:zotero.org:groups:5435545:items:68YK2XWS"}, {"identifier": "10.1159/000065938"}], "communities": [{"id": "batlit"}, {"id": "biosyslit"}], "relations": {"version": [{"index": 0, "is_last": true, "parent": {"pid_